Class DateTimeFiltersImpl

java.lang.Object
com.example.OpenWeatherProject.filters.DateTimeFiltersImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
DateTimeFilters
public class DateTimeFiltersImpl extends Object implements DateTimeFilters
This class contains the methods necessary to filter the data according to a time range chosen by the user, and print them on the terminal.
